src.main
Routines that are shared by different radiative transfer versions.

-- 1D model files --
main.F90                    - model driver
input.F90                   - model input 
output.F90                  - model output

-- 3D model files --
exo_radiation_cam_intr.F90  - shared interface for operation with CAM
mcica.F90                   - shared monte carlo independent cloud approximation
mcica_random_numbers.F90    - shared mcica routines

-- 1D/3D shared
exo_init_ref.F90            - initialize certain parameters
exo_radiation_mod.F90       - two stream radiative transfer
rayleigh_data.F90 	    - rayleigh scattering parameters
planck.F90		    - planck function function
sys_rootdir.F90		    - system directories 
